Visit Moonwell: Go to card.moonwell.fi and click “Get your card.”

Connect Your Wallet: Choose from over 350 wallet options, including Coinbase Wallet, MetaMask, Rabby, or Cypher Wallet.

Complete KYC Verification: Provide personal details and verify your identity through Cypher WalletD Inc. This streamlined process typically takes under five minutes.

Verify Email and Set Up Telegram: Confirm your email address and link your Telegram account for real-time updates.

Select Card Design: Choose a design for your digital Moonwell Card.

Load and Spend: Load USDC from your wallet or borrow against supplied assets, then start spending instantly.

